    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Hakaiton Clan, Level 8+ <br />Your jutsu are more likely to disintegrate, even in their base forms. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Constitution or Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>Jutsu you cast with the Fire or Lightning Release keyword do not need to deal necrotic damage to cause objects to disintegrate.</li><li>Necrotic damage you deal does double damage to structures. This can stack with other doubling effects.</li></ul>",
